Package: libcatalina-1.0-0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: GObject library for asynchronous key/value storage - shared libraries
 Catalina is an asynchronous library for basic key/value storage.  It includes
 compact serializers, compression, and encryption.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries.

Package: libcatalina-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libcatalina-1.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         libglib2.0-dev (>= 2.16.0)
Suggests: libunique-doc, vala
Description: GObject library for asynchronous key/value storage - development files
 Catalina is an asynchronous library for basic key/value storage.  It includes
 compact serializers, compression, and encryption.
 .
 This package contains the headers and development libraries needed to
 build applications using the Catalina library

Package: libcatalina-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libcatalina-1.0-0
Suggests: devhelp
Description: GObject library for asynchronous key/value storage - documentation
 Catalina is an asynchronous library for basic key/value storage.  It includes
 compact serializers, compression, and encryption.
 .
 This package contains the HTML documentation for the Catalina library

